{"tid":856783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[萬億填海] 小心拆屋效應","createTime":"2018-10-10T18:43:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T03:12:35.000Z","uid":1654,"like":57,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"54816d8b8ea9c77a4542ce18758be4c52950b3ef","tid":856783,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T18:43:25.000Z","msg":"'''魯迅（周樹人）在1927年所寫的《無聲的中國》中寫道：「中國人的性情總是喜歡調和、折中的，譬如你說，這屋子太暗，說在這裏開一個天窗，大家一定是不允許的。但如果你主張拆掉屋頂，他們就會來調和，願意開天窗了。」。這種效應由此而得名「拆屋效應」[1]，也被稱為「破天窗效應」[2]。'''<br />\n<br />\n小心比人開天殺價，落地還錢。<br />\n推個好撚誇張既方案出黎，明知社會好難接受都推，<br />\n然後推個3000 億既方案出黎，<br />\n好多on9 見好似平好多就轉軚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n鳩鐵千億已經冇人提話好撚貴好有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e3166adc1d919e383e1a8bee4bb5ed7f461a934","tid":856783,"uid":1654,"like":12,"dislike":5,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T16:16:47.000Z","msg":"建築師行倡「藍塘」取代東大嶼都會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/860358\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/860358</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家成班連登仔就覺得比1000 億出黎起比將來20 年既支那人好合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52ba5a59345e1276eaf0a1783886b0fd43e59059","tid":856783,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T17:03:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ebe59217babb1c3441dd2c3c190ce375efdf73b","tid":856783,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T17:34:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/a